* [[The Ark (Stargate Atlantis)|"The Ark" (''Stargate Atlantis'')]], an episode of ''Stargate Atlantis''
* [[Ark (Noon Universe)]], a fictional planet in a series of novels by Arkady and Boris Strugatsky
* [[Ark (Baxter novel)|''Ark'' (Baxter novel)]], a 2009 hard science fiction novel
* ''[[Ark II]]'', a children's science fiction television series
* ''ARK'' (1996), a book of poetry by [[Ronald Johnson (poet)|Ronald Johnson]]

